thread.title: Agnieszka Radwanska wins Tianjin Open
thread.title_full: Agnieszka Radwanska wins Tianjin Open - Sports

author: AFP
title: Agnieszka Radwanska wins Tianjin Open
text:
Beijing: Poland's Agnieszka Radwanska secured a slot in the WTA Finals with a straight-sets victory in the final of China's Tianjin Open yesterday.


Agnieszka Radwanska of Poland poses with her trophy after winning the women's singles final match against Danka Kovinic of Montenegro at the Tianjin Open tennis tournament in Tianjin. Pic/AFP 
The 6-1, 6-2 win by the World No 6 over the much lower ranked Montenegrin Danka Kovinic ensures her place at the WTA Finals in Singapore next month.
The second-seed broke five times without being broken herself to dismiss Kovinic in just 58 minutes.
